Create:
curl -X POST http://localhost:4567/tasks \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"title":"Read Sinatra docs","description":"Learn routing","status":"pending"}'

List:
curl http://localhost:4567/tasks

Get one:
curl http://localhost:4567/tasks/1

Update:
curl -X PUT http://localhost:4567/tasks/1 \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"status":"done"}'

Delete:
curl -X DELETE http://localhost:4567/tasks/1


Error Handling


404 if task not found:


{ "error": "Task not found" }



400 invalid JSON body:


{ "error": "Invalid JSON body" }



422 validation errors:


{ "error": "Title is required" }


Future Improvements (Optional)


Add pagination to /tasks


Add search/filter by status


Add authentication (JWT)


Add AI feature: generate a study pla
